How to Rock Haouse of Indya Ethnic Wear at Work:
Ever considered wearing ethnic attire to work but immediately discarded the notion because you believed it wouldn't look good? Here's how to rock the ethnic appearance with our must-have fusion wear items!
The Modern Muse- For a chic and fuss-free fusion style, team a cold shoulder maxi tunic with a simple wide belt.
The Minimalist- According to The Minimalist, simplicity is in! Put on a cowl-hemmed or high-low tunic and accessories with a tidy updo.
The Boho Chic: Add a boho twist to your ethnic appearance by pairing a basic palazzo and crop top with a longline jacket tunic.
Some Ethnic Wear Styling Tips to Swear By:
Confused about accessorizing and styling? Here are some tips for you 
Always wear bright-colored clothes:
Festivals are all about ethnic clothing, which one can easily wear to work. Wearing vibrant colors is so essential because they appear energizing and vibrant.
Layer jackets:
On top of your solid kurtas, add an overlay. This would make your outfit look more contemporary. You can make a statement by wearing it with women's kurta sets bought online.
Accessorize your look:
You should always accessorize your outfit. It gives your clothing a more energized appearance. But you ought to be able to strike a balance. You can include nose rings, bindis, earrings, bangles, and more.
Wearing a denim jacket as a covering:
You may also wear an oxidized necklace with your ethnic kurta and a denim jacket over it. Again, it provides your ensemble with a contemporary appearance with a traditional twist.
Ideal clothing fits:
Knowing which size will suit you exactly can help you feel wonderful and more confident. You can use the sizing chart on our website to choose the ideal size for you.
Selecting the ideal footwear to go with the look:
Wearing the right shoes with your attire is essential. You can wear a dress with both heels and booty when wearing a kurta set, a kurta when wearing heels, or both when wearing a kurta.
The Bottom Line:
Ethnic wear is the need of every woman and the House of Indya is here for that. You can now order the latest Indya collection online from the Distacart.com website with benefits like express delivery and reasonable rates.

Horlicks: The Health Drink that Fuels Your Mornings and Unwinds Your Evenings!
As a child our most favorite and happy go-to everyday drink is Horlicks, and our mother’s confident choice of drink too. Whether it's our morning energizer or evening stress reliever, Horlicks stands as one of the best health drinks we can enjoy. It is one of the most accepted brands for its brand equity in health drinks, primarily recognized by its nutritious value and acceptance among different age groups. It was invented during the late 19th century by James and William Horlick as a malt-based drink with changes to fit the nutritional requirements for the growing child, adults, and elderly people.
Horlicks is a brand, the name of which strikes different flavors and formulations in most homes across large parts of the globe, but mainly India and South Asia. In this blog, we shall discuss the latest in Horlicks—its health benefits, the ingredients, and different variants available.
If you are thinking of buying a Horlicks drink then Distacart.com is your destination. You can shop according to your needs and preferences from the plethora of options available on our website.  
What is Horlicks?
Horlicks is a malted milk powder that, with a mix of milk or hot water, forms a nutritious health supplement. It promotes growth, develops better bones, and supplements vital nutrients within the body. Over these years, Horlicks has been adding into the product line different age groups such as those of children, women, and adults, and is going to launch special variants that suit the needs arising out of the different groupings.
It is a product with a history of clinical success and is nutrient-rich. It multiplies the milk's beneficial components, which makes it extremely beneficial for children's or pregnant ladies’ development. Additionally, there are other flavors and varieties of Horlicks on the market. Here are a few examples.
Nutritional Value of Horlicks:
Horlicks has been enriched with many types of vitamins and minerals to increase the nutritive value to the daily schedule and is capturing the attention of families for its nutrition purpose. Some of the major health benefits include:
Better Bone Health: The calcium and Vitamin D in Horlicks are good for a person's bones. This is most important at the growth stage, both in children and aged adults. 
Brain Development: The brand informs us that Horlicks is fortified with DHA, an Omega-3 fatty acid forming an important ingredient in developing a child's brain.
Tougher Immunity: It contains necessary vitamins like A, C, and E which help enhance the immunity of the children so as to toughen them against illnesses.
Energy Boost: With ingredients like malted barley and wheat, Horlicks provides sustained energy throughout the day and hence is a favorite among people as a drink for starting one's day.
Micronutrients: It contains iron and zinc, which are important for one's health in carrying oxygen throughout the body and even the repair of cells.
What are the Major Ingredients in Horlicks?
The following are some of the primary components of Horlicks.


Malted Barley- Horlicks contains 39% malted barley. Bareilly contains a lot of fiber, vitamins, and minerals.

Wheat Flour- Up to 25% of it is made up of wheat flour. Numerous vitamins and minerals are also included in it, in addition to fiber.

Milk Solids- This ingredient contains up to 14% milk powder. The primary source of calcium and protein is milk.

Wheat Gluten- Another protein found in it is wheat gluten.

Sugar- Sweet malted milk also contains sugar as a flavoring.

Minerals- There are numerous significant minerals in it.

Vitamins- It also contains a number of vital vitamins in addition to minerals.

Salt- Salt has also been used in modest amounts.

Soy- Soy protein is added to increase protein intake.

Including all these, Horlicks has curated drinks for different age groups, keeping in mind the different needs.
Horlicks - Popular Variants on Distacart.com:
Horlicks Health And Nutrition Classic Malt 
This is the classic and basic Horlicks drink which is unflavored. It increases calcium consumption in children and helps their bones grow stronger. Horlicks drink is clinically proven to increase the lean tissues, hence making the muscles stronger. It also boosts concentration and helps the children focus more.

